title: Artist Tristan Eaton
description:
Tiston Eaton is a multi-talented artist. He once designed a crazy wrap for Matt's Mini Cooper. Before that he was a graffiti artist. And since then he has designed toys and graphics for famous companies like Kid Robot, sold paintings and been hired to create amazing mural work. 

See Triston's amazing work here: https://tristaneaton.com/

 

T: @thesmokingtire, @zackklapman @tristaneaton

IG: @thesmokingtire, @fakezackklapman @tristaneaton

 

WATCH the show! https://youtu.be/gcxyuI0d0f4
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
